MR. BHUSAN TRIVEDI

Founder of Piconery

Through the Myanmar Stoves Campaign, he played his part in positively impacting more than 200,000 lives in rural Myanmar, And creating 1000+ local jobs for men and women, and avoiding around 250,000 Tones of CO2 emissions left out in the environment due to cooking using firewood in open-fires/three-stone stoves.
